inds|Applied Minds LLC]], and [[Walt Disney Imagineering]] *[[John Gaburick]] of [[Impact Wrestling]] *[[Hugh Hefner]] of [[Playboy Enterprises]]<ref>[http://www.biography.com/people/hugh-hefner-9333521#synopsis "Hugh Hefner Biography"]</ref> *[[Geoff Johns]] of [[DC Entertainment]]<ref>[http://www.dcentertainment.com/management/geoff-johns "Geoff Johns"]</ref> *[[Jared Leto]] of [[Fandor (film site)|Fandor]] *[[Hisao Oguchi]] of [[Sega Sammy Holdings]] *[[Joe Quesada]] of [[Marvel Entertainment]] *[[Will.I.Am]] of [[3D Systems]] <ref>{{cite web|title=3D Systems Appoints will.i.am as Its Chief Creative Officer|url=http://www.3dsystems.com/press-releases/3d-systems-appoints-william-its-chief-creative-officer|website=3D Systems|accessdate=12 April 2016}}</ref>
